Creepy Sean
This man was charged on several accounts for stalking and harassing a young college student. Eventually there was a lawsuit and restraining order put into effect. 

This is an actual picture where he photoshopped a picture of his face on top of her boyfriend's face and sent it to her. Eventually she was fed up with all the commotion.
